{"tid":2518360,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"職場霸凌風波！《巫師3》開發總監宣布辭職","createTime":"2021-05-06T03:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T03:50:56.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c21de37d7470fd01c574e073dcc0c5f3b02509df","tid":2518360,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:32:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-05-05/570173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-05-05%2F570173&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQtDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=4cd38db9\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-05-05/570173</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRpdWKAeJHW6g5sEtncP4AwHsM9gVtMYrKR7o3pDvRvB9?filename=AOY50ja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOY50ja.jpg&h=56e54825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾擔任《巫師3：狂獵》遊戲總監、《電馭叛客2077》開發副總監及產品負責人的Konrad Tomaszkiewicz因職場霸凌問題，今（5）日宣布將離開待了17年的CD Projekt RED。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Konrad遭CDPR內部人員控訴其職場霸凌的問題，經過了數個月的調查後，公司正式宣布他無罪，對此Konrad本人也是打從一開始就否認霸凌之說。儘管內部調查已證實Konrad無罪，他依舊因為同事與他之間的嫌隙選擇離開CDPR。對此他表示：「即使證明我無罪，還是有很多人對與我共事感到害怕、壓力與不適，我為所有因我而起的仇恨道歉。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf1sn1xLpXzepSBmtRjTfk7edsux4jZ9uLA32JRHEthsn?filename=pNQTpL2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNQTpL2.jpg&h=9e0403c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">Konrad在CDPR工作了17年，參與過《巫師》系列所有作品的製作。 圖：翻攝自Konrad Tomaszkiewicz LinkedIn</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">在離開CDPR後，Konrad將以個人身份工作，他說道：「要改變個性是個長期而辛苦的過程，但我不會放棄的，因為我希望自己可以有所改變。」</span>根據Konrad在國外知名商務社群網站LinkedIn上的資歷表，他於2004年以遊戲測試員的身分加入CDPR，參與過所有《巫師》系列作品的製作，《巫師3》上市後取得的巨大成功，Konrad可說是功不可沒。<br />\n<br />\n據彭博社的消息指出，Konrad原本預計將在2022年新的《巫師》系列作中擔綱製作要角，對於此時離開CDPR他表示相當遺憾。而在Konrad離職前不久，《電馭叛客 2077》的首席設計師Andrzej Zawadzki才於3月22日宣布離開合作了8年的CDPR，資深員工相繼出走也令外界相當關注CDPR未來的人事重組。"},{"pid":"408d5f0e23fbcbeff0b8fc90ec6d0013b1d46d12","tid":2518360,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"巫師3真心悶，連登仔打機品味唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"9c0fe22b4e43aaaa4fb57ea8b336f37132deb44b","tid":2518360,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVpkxxRLwXCfUDW1wbxSd3psLfRcuaF6qxoEbgbqLa37H?filename=NYxeTGO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYxeTGO.jpg&h=a8f77efd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57d06847e93b480f40408f4b8635b7d8c6814f07","tid":2518360,"uid":220431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"408d5f0e23fbcbeff0b8fc90ec6d0013b1d46d12","tid":2518360,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"巫師3真心悶，連登仔打機品味唔識欣賞"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"唔係下下唱下反調 就以為自己好識貨先得"},{"pid":"fa6dee49fdf06993c51dfa9a4b2566b369a36c3a","tid":2518360,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"57d06847e93b480f40408f4b8635b7d8c6814f07","tid":2518360,"uid":220431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"408d5f0e23fbcbeff0b8fc90ec6d0013b1d46d12","tid":2518360,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"巫師3真心悶，連登仔打機品味唔識欣賞"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"唔係下下唱下反調 就以為自己好識貨先得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"悶=唱反調<br />\n<br />\n咁話垃圾係咪=搞革命"},{"pid":"b42f0cfa4bcf60619d09bcf63582d9fdbfd31707","tid":2518360,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa6dee49fdf06993c51dfa9a4b2566b369a36c3a","tid":2518360,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"57d06847e93b480f40408f4b8635b7d8c6814f07","tid":2518360,"uid":220431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"408d5f0e23fbcbeff0b8fc90ec6d0013b1d46d12","tid":2518360,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"